-Let me go! I have to.

00:32.281 --> 00:35.327
No! We got to save her, Mama! We got to!

00:35.410 --> 00:38.247
-No! Stop! Stop it! Stop it, baby.
-No! Let me go!

00:40.082 --> 00:42.751
Pity! Pity! Pity!

00:43.293 --> 00:45.212
Maude! Maude!

00:45.295 --> 00:46.296
Help!

00:49.216 --> 00:51.426
Pity! Pity!

00:54.388 --> 00:55.639
Pity!

00:58.267 --> 00:59.268
Pity.

01:01.979 --> 01:03.230
Pity.

01:03.313 --> 01:05.065
Don't be scared, Maude.

01:05.649 --> 01:07.317
Don't be scared. Come on.

01:25.002 --> 01:29.298
No, no. No, get off! Get off me!

01:30.340 --> 01:31.800
Please. Baby!

01:31.884 --> 01:33.468
Let me get my baby!

01:34.970 --> 01:37.431
Let me go get my baby!

01:37.514 --> 01:40.517
My baby! Somebody get my baby!

01:41.351 --> 01:43.353
