02:53.173 --> 02:54.633
Good morning.

02:54.716 --> 02:56.426
Hey.

02:59.471 --> 03:00.639
Oh, you feel hot.

03:02.516 --> 03:04.309
Been running through fire.

03:06.562 --> 03:08.522
