03:08.605 --> 03:11.441
My little girlfriend, Maude Petit,
was in there, about to burn up.

03:11.525 --> 03:13.360
I run in and saved her.

03:13.443 --> 03:15.487
That sound like
a good dream this time.

03:15.571 --> 03:20.492
I don't know if I'd call it that,
but it was a long time coming.

03:20.576 --> 03:24.788
Yeah, well, whatever it was,
you seem nice and calm. That's new.

03:24.872 --> 03:27.040
Yeah, well, not up here.

03:29.835 --> 03:33.839
I remember 54, 55 years ago,

03:33.922 --> 03:39.428
I was reading this comic book about Thor,
Norse god of thunder.

03:40.929 --> 03:45.392
His old man, Odin,
had a-- a chair, a throne.

03:46.560 --> 03:49.980
Throne was named Hlidskjalf.

03:51.356 --> 03:53.400
And when Odin sat on that throne,

03:53.483 --> 03:59.781
he could see everything,
everywhere, all at once.

04:01.909 --> 04:03.619
That's how I feel up here.

04:04.578 --> 04:10.250
Maude and my mama. Sensia. You.

04:10.334 --> 04:11.335
Me?

04:12.252 --> 04:13.712
You ain't even known me a month.

04:15.881 --> 04:19.384
Wouldn't be no me sitting here
if you wasn't sitting next to me.

04:23.555 --> 04:24.806
Is I'm still hot?

04:25.849 --> 04:28.810
Yeah. Take some of this water.

04:30.604 --> 04:31.730
It's for your pill.

04:34.525 --> 04:35.984
I'm gonna go take a shower.

04:38.153 --> 04:39.821
