04:41.448 --> 04:44.284
W-R-I-N-G!

04:44.368 --> 04:45.369
Yes.

04:56.338 --> 04:57.339
Hello?

04:57.422 --> 04:59.258
It's me, Ptolemy.

04:59.341 --> 05:01.718
I knew who it was.

05:01.802 --> 05:04.012
I knew it was you before the phone rang.

05:04.096 --> 05:06.098
What can I do for you, Ms. Wring?

05:06.640 --> 05:09.351
-You can say "yes."
-Yes.

05:09.434 --> 05:12.187
Don't you even wanna know
what you saying yes about?

05:12.271 --> 05:13.397
Sure I do,

05:13.480 --> 05:17.192
