on that count.

07:00.754 --> 07:02.130
Hi.

07:06.677 --> 07:07.761
How you doing?

07:07.845 --> 07:09.805
-Fine, you?
-Good.

07:17.104 --> 07:18.856
-You all right?
-Yeah, I'm fine.

08:01.732 --> 08:03.192
Hey, Pitypapa.

08:05.277 --> 08:11.533
