08:19.291 --> 08:24.505
I'd get us up before the sun.

08:27.633 --> 08:31.220
Take the bus down to Lake Altoona.

08:33.764 --> 08:38.684
We'd take off our socks and shoes,
walk down to the shoreline,

08:39.477 --> 08:41.563
watch the sunrise.

08:41.647 --> 08:42.898
That all?

08:45.359 --> 08:46.985
Then we'd go to a museum,

08:48.111 --> 08:50.822
