08:59.957 --> 09:00.958
Yeah.

09:56.930 --> 09:57.931
Mr. Grey.

09:59.266 --> 10:00.267
Good morning.

10:12.863 --> 10:15.240
-What's your name?
-Hernandez.

10:16.033 --> 10:17.701
Pleased to meet you, Mr. Hernandez.

10:17.784 --> 10:20.704
No, Mr. Grey.
Not Mr. Hernandez, just Hernandez.

10:20.787 --> 10:22.039
I like that name.

10:22.915 --> 10:26.877
-You from around these parts, Hernandez?
-40 years here. Thirty-eight, really.

10:26.960 --> 10:30.797
When I was seven, my parents came up
from a farm in the south of Mexico.

10:30.881 --> 10:32.216
Still speak Spanish?

10:32.299 --> 10:34.885
